ury. Brain Eno called those flashes of communal genius &#8220;scenius.&#822=
1; Throughout history, scenius has been limited by whoever happened to live=
 in, or could afford to move to, a given place in a given time. Pre-COVID, =
even with billions of people online, we didn&#8217;t have the tools or norm=
s necessary to capture the ineffable magic of IRL digitally.&nbsp;</p><p st=
